tag_list: software-development-proposal, software-project-proposal, project-proposal, software-proposals, proposal-software, proposal-template, project-proposal-sample, software-project-estimation, project-proposal-template, proposals-software, project-estimator
overview: SWproposal is an automated tool for creating professional and elegant software project proposals. An easy, fast, and professional way to generate man-hour estimates and create elegant proposals for software development projects. The CRM functionality keeps track of daily sales activity, maintains a list of potential and current clients with a negotiation history, stores all related files and documents, helps to generate appointments, etc. - all in one system for software development company or freelancers.
